03:56.923 --> 03:59.626
IF ANYTHING HAPPENS TO ME,
GIVE IT TO VERONICA.

03:59.626 --> 04:02.268
I WILL.

04:02.268 --> 04:05.171
YOU DON'T HAVE ANYTHING
TO SAY ABOUT IT?

04:05.171 --> 04:08.575
