13:23.489 --> 13:24.825
BUT I KNOW MY WIFE.

13:24.825 --> 13:27.661
SHE'LL COOL OFF.
SHE'LL BE BACK, SO RELAX.

13:27.661 --> 13:29.830
HAS SHE DONE THIS BEFORE?

13:29.830 --> 13:31.364
NO.

13:31.364 --> 13:33.166
THEN HOW DO YOU KNOW
WHAT SHE'LL DO NOW?

13:33.166 --> 13:35.435
DAVID,
MY WIFE IS LIKE AN ANIMAL

13:35.435 --> 13:37.103
THAT WAS RAISED
IN CAPTIVITY, OKAY?

13:37.103 --> 13:39.105
SHE'S NOT GONNA BE ABLE
TO SURVIVE VERY LONG

13:39.105 --> 13:40.140
OUT IN THE WILD.

13:40.140 --> 13:41.508
SHE'LL CALM DOWN,
SHE'LL BE BACK.

13:41.508 --> 13:42.509
RELAX.

13:42.509 --> 13:43.810
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

13:43.810 --> 13:44.978
COME IN.

13:44.978 --> 13:46.279
KNOCK, KNOCK.

13:46.279 --> 13:47.648
WELL.

13:47.648 --> 13:49.115
WELL, HELLO, SWEETHEART.

13:49.115 --> 13:50.751
HONEY.

13:50.751 --> 13:53.286
WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?

13:53.286 --> 13:55.321
WELL, IF I HAD SEEN YOU
AT BREAKFAST,

13:55.321 --> 13:57.157
YOU WOULD KNOW
WHAT WAS GOING ON.

13:57.157 --> 13:59.125
UH...
JIM.

13:59.125 --> 14:00.393
VERONICA.

14:00.393 --> 14:02.636
I HAD TO LEAVE EARLY.
I HAD A MEETING.

14:02.636 --> 14:04.337
THAT WOULD BE MY FAULT.

14:04.337 --> 14:06.673
AH.

14:06.673 --> 14:08.274
I SEE.

14:08.274 --> 14:09.475
POLITICS.

14:09.475 --> 14:11.044
GUILTY AS CHARGED.

14:11.044 --> 14:12.478
BUT LOOK AT YOU.

14:12.478 --> 14:14.280
WHAT BRINGS YOU
TO THE HALLS OF JUSTICE?

14:14.280 --> 14:15.649
YOU REALLY MISS IT
THAT MUCH?

14:15.649 --> 14:17.884
ACTUALLY,
I DON'T MISS IT AT ALL.

14:17.884 --> 14:19.520
GOOD.

14:19.520 --> 14:20.887
BUT I'VE BEEN CALLED
TO DUTY.

14:20.887 --> 14:22.789
MEANING?

14:22.789 --> 14:25.692
KATHERYN HAS ASKED ME TO HELP
HANNA'S SON.

14:25.692 --> 14:28.294
REALLY?

14:28.294 --> 14:29.830
IS THAT A FACT?

14:29.830 --> 14:31.297
YES.

14:31.297 --> 14:33.967
THAT'S WHAT I WANTED TO TELL YOU
BEFORE YOU LEFT THIS MORNING.

14:33.967 --> 14:36.469
NOW, WHY IN THE WORLD
WOULD YOU WANT TO DO THAT?

14:36.469 --> 14:39.305
SHE ASKED.

14:39.305 --> 14:41.007
AND IT LOOKED
SIMPLE ENOUGH.

14:41.007 --> 14:44.177
APPARENTLY,
HER SON'S A DRUG DEALER.

14:44.177 --> 14:46.346
I'M NOT SO SURE.

14:46.346 --> 14:48.515
HE'S CLEAN, NO PRIORS.

14:48.515 --> 14:50.951
I CAN'T REALLY SAY
WHAT'S GOING ON,

14:50.951 --> 14:52.886
BUT I KNOW
IT'S SOMETHING.

14:52.886 --> 14:54.821
ARREST WAS SOLID.

14:54.821 --> 14:59.804
I MEAN, THE BOY HAD TWO KILOS
OF NARCOTICS IN HIS POSSESSION.

15:00.994 --> 15:03.036
HOW DO YOU KNOW SO MUCH
ABOUT THIS?

15:03.036 --> 15:06.239
OH, I, UH, I ASKED DAVID
TO HELP HANNA.

15:06.239 --> 15:07.674
YES.

15:07.674 --> 15:10.343
AND, UH,
I READ THE ARREST REPORT.

15:10.343 --> 15:12.779
I REALLY DON'T WANT YOU
INVOLVED IN THIS.

15:12.779 --> 15:14.280
WELL, IT'S TOO LATE.

15:14.280 --> 15:15.281
[ CHUCKLES ]

15:15.281 --> 15:16.683
HONEY, DON'T.

15:16.683 --> 15:19.720
DON'T WORRY ABOUT ME.

15:22.756 --> 15:25.425
IT WAS A PRESSURE
OF THE LAW

15:25.425 --> 15:29.630
THAT CAUSED YOU TO HAVE
THAT PROBLEM IN THE PAST.

15:29.630 --> 15:31.598
WHY DON'T I
LEAVE YOU TWO ALONE?

15:31.598 --> 15:32.599
THIS IS PRIVATE.

15:32.599 --> 15:33.700
NO.

15:33.700 --> 15:36.302
YOU'RE FAMILY.

15:36.302 --> 15:39.372
IT WAS HURTING MY BACK

15:39.372 --> 15:42.242
THAT CAUSED ME TO START TAKING
THE PAIN KILLERS

15:42.242 --> 15:43.644
THAT I BECAME ADDICTED TO.

15:43.644 --> 15:46.547
BUT YOU COULDN'T STOP.

15:46.547 --> 15:48.749
I'M FINE.

15:48.749 --> 15:52.152
HONEY,
I DON'T WANT YOU TO DO THIS.

15:52.152 --> 15:53.286
IT'S BEEN THREE YEARS.

15:53.286 --> 15:55.155
IT'LL BE GOOD TO GET
IN THE FIGHT AGAIN.

15:55.155 --> 15:56.156
SWEETHEART.

15:56.156 --> 15:58.324
DAVID, PLEASE, STOP IT.

15:58.324 --> 16:00.226
SERIOUSLY, I'M ‐‐
I'M GONNA GET SOME WATER,

16:00.226 --> 16:01.467
SOME COFFEE, SOMETHING.

16:01.467 --> 16:03.436
NO.
CONTINUE YOUR MEETING.

16:03.436 --> 16:06.973
I HAVE TO GO MEET WITH
THE DETECTIVE WHO DID THE BUST.

16:06.973 --> 16:09.643
I HAVE BEEN LOOKING AT THIS CASE
ALL NIGHT,

16:09.643 --> 16:12.779
AND SOME THINGS
JUST DON'T ADD UP.

16:12.779 --> 16:15.348
HMM.

16:15.348 --> 16:18.284
I WILL SEE YOU AT HOME.

16:18.284 --> 16:19.786
YES, YOU WILL.

16:19.786 --> 16:21.187
JIM.

16:21.187 --> 16:23.356
VERONICA.

16:30.697 --> 16:31.898
DAVID.

16:31.898 --> 16:33.199
I KNOW.

16:33.199 --> 16:35.636
DAMN IT, I KNOW.

16:43.443 --> 16:45.512
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

16:54.721 --> 16:56.790
HI.

16:58.058 --> 16:59.693
WHAT DO YOU WANT?

16:59.693 --> 17:01.167
WYATT WANTED TO STOP BY.

17:03.136 --> 17:05.672
UM, NOW IS NOT A GOOD TIME.
SORRY.

17:05.672 --> 17:08.074
WHY?
WAITING FOR A JOHN?

17:08.074 --> 17:10.911
I'M BUSY.

17:10.911 --> 17:12.345
WHERE'S AMANDA?

17:12.345 --> 17:14.715
CLASS.
SHE'S STUDYING.

17:14.715 --> 17:16.082
OKAY.

17:16.082 --> 17:17.751
WE'LL WAIT FOR HER THEN.

17:17.751 --> 17:18.952
NO, YOU WON'T.

17:18.952 --> 17:20.521
I HAVE THINGS TO DO.

17:20.521 --> 17:21.888
LIKE WHAT?

17:21.888 --> 17:26.492
JEFFREY, GET YOUR BOY
AND PUT HIM ON A LEASH.

17:27.761 --> 17:29.796
[ SCOFFS ]

17:29.796 --> 17:31.264
LEASH?

17:31.264 --> 17:34.835
WYATT, I'M NOT IN THE MOOD
FOR THIS TODAY.

17:34.835 --> 17:35.836
GOODBYE.

17:35.836 --> 17:39.172
COME ON, MAN.
SHE'S NOT HERE.

17:40.707 --> 17:42.643
OKAY, GO.
I DON'T HAVE TIME FOR THIS.

17:42.643 --> 17:45.245
THAT'S RIGHT.

17:45.245 --> 17:47.147
YOU CHARGE BY THE MINUTE.

17:48.782 --> 17:50.183
EXCUSE ME?

17:50.183 --> 17:51.785
$1,000 AN HOUR?

17:51.785 --> 17:52.853
HEY, WYATT.

17:52.853 --> 17:54.387
WHAT?

17:54.387 --> 17:56.757
YOU TOLD ME YOU WANTED TO COME
HERE TO CHECK ON YOUR SISTER.

17:56.757 --> 17:58.024
SHE'S NOT HERE,
SO LET'S GO.

17:58.024 --> 17:59.560
YES, GO.

17:59.560 --> 18:03.203
LISTEN TO THE PERSON WHO THINKS
AND SPEAKS FOR YOU.

18:03.203 --> 18:04.538
IT WOULD BE WISE.

18:04.538 --> 18:06.139
AND YOU DON'T HAVE TO
INSULT HIM.

18:07.874 --> 18:10.343
PROTECTIVE, ISN'T SHE?
HMM?

18:12.012 --> 18:14.147
I'M DONE. LET'S GO.

18:14.147 --> 18:16.349
I AM.

18:16.349 --> 18:18.018
BUT FIRST,
I WANT TO TALK TO CANDACE.

18:19.820 --> 18:22.556
IS MY SISTER IN THIS?

18:22.556 --> 18:24.791
IN WHAT?
PROSTITUTION.

18:24.791 --> 18:27.393
OH, MY GOODNESS,
JEFFREY.

18:27.393 --> 18:29.830
I THOUGHT YOU WERE HELPING
THIS BOY GET OFF OF CRACK.

18:29.830 --> 18:31.965
HEROIN.
SAME THING.

18:31.965 --> 18:33.399
IT'S ALL FOR THE WEAK.

18:33.399 --> 18:35.168
[ SCOFFS ]

18:35.168 --> 18:36.970
WYATT ‐‐
SHUT UP, JEFFREY.

18:36.970 --> 18:38.371
OKAY.

18:38.371 --> 18:40.273
IS MY SISTER IN THIS?

18:40.273 --> 18:42.876
YOU'RE ASSUMING I AM.

18:44.044 --> 18:46.980
THIS IS YOU.

18:46.980 --> 18:49.115
CANDY?

18:49.115 --> 18:50.316
911?

18:50.316 --> 18:52.819
$1,000.

18:52.819 --> 18:54.555
STILL WANT TO DENY IT?

18:55.656 --> 18:57.991
QUIET NOW, AREN'T WE?

18:57.991 --> 18:59.359
YES.

18:59.359 --> 19:02.869
THIS IS WHAT I DO FROM TIME
TO TIME TO MAKE A LIVING.

19:02.869 --> 19:03.870
WHAT?

19:03.870 --> 19:05.972
YOU'RE JUDGING ME,
MR. HEROIN?

19:05.972 --> 19:09.309
I GREW UP WITH NOTHING.

19:09.309 --> 19:11.845
I DIDN'T HAVE A SILVER SPOON
IN MY MOUTH.

19:11.845 --> 19:13.880
SO YOU PUT SOMETHING ELSE
IN IT.

19:13.880 --> 19:15.448
YES.

19:15.448 --> 19:17.350
AND I'M VERY GOOD AT IT.

19:17.350 --> 19:22.488
YOU HAVE BEEN GIVEN EVERYTHING
AND YOU ALWAYS BLOW IT.

19:22.488 --> 19:24.357
APPARENTLY, SO DO YOU.

19:24.357 --> 19:27.293
YOU HAVE HAD THE WORLD
HANDED TO YOU,

19:27.293 --> 19:30.496
AND IF YOU DON'T GET OUT
OF MY APARTMENT,

19:30.496 --> 19:32.398
I WILL HAND YOU YOUR ASS.

19:32.398 --> 19:33.634
COME ON, WYATT.
GET.

19:33.634 --> 19:35.802
I'M NOT GOING ANYWHERE
UNTIL I FIND MY SISTER.

19:35.802 --> 19:37.571
SHE'S NOT ANSWERING
MY PHONE CALLS.

19:37.571 --> 19:40.240
SHE KNOW ABOUT YOU?

19:40.240 --> 19:44.645
IF YOU DON'T LEAVE
RIGHT NOW...

19:44.645 --> 19:45.879
GO.

19:45.879 --> 19:47.047
OKAY.

19:47.047 --> 19:49.049
WYATT! WYATT!
WYATT! WYATT!

19:49.049 --> 19:50.250
NO!

19:50.250 --> 19:52.185
WYATT, WAIT!

19:52.185 --> 19:54.020
WHY IS THIS ROOM
SUCH A MESS?

19:56.256 --> 19:58.358
WHAT'S GOING ON,
CANDACE?

20:14.214 --> 20:17.283
SO?

20:17.283 --> 20:20.787
VERONICA IS INTO THIS.

20:22.689 --> 20:24.791
AND WHAT ARE YOU GONNA DO
ABOUT THAT?

20:24.791 --> 20:28.595
WHAT DO YOU MEAN
WHAT AM I GOING TO DO?

20:28.595 --> 20:30.230
COME ON, DAVID.
WE BOTH KNOW VERONICA.

20:30.230 --> 20:31.665
WHAT ARE YOU GONNA DO
ABOUT THAT?

20:31.665 --> 20:33.366
YES, WE DO.

20:33.366 --> 20:34.768
YES, AND WE BOTH KNOW

20:34.768 --> 20:36.803
THAT ONCE VERONICA GETS HER NOSE
INTO SOMETHING,

20:36.803 --> 20:38.104
SHE'S GOING TO KEEP IT THERE

20:38.104 --> 20:40.373
UNTIL SHE UNCOVERS EVERY BONE
THAT WE HAVE BURIED,

20:40.373 --> 20:44.110
SO AGAIN, I SAY WHAT ARE YOU
GOING TO DO ABOUT THAT?

20:44.110 --> 20:47.080
I AM AWARE OF THAT.

20:48.849 --> 20:53.119
SO, ARE YOU GOING TO COME UP
WITH SOMETHING?

20:53.119 --> 20:55.656
YES, I WILL.

20:57.457 --> 21:00.634
YOU'RE NOT CONCERNED.
YOU'RE NOT PANICKED AT ALL.

21:00.634 --> 21:01.668
WHY?

21:01.668 --> 21:03.403
JIM...
NO, NO, NO.

21:03.403 --> 21:05.471
YOU ALREADY HAVE A PLAN,
DON'T YOU?

21:05.471 --> 21:07.674
[ CHUCKLES ]
NO, I DON'T.

21:07.674 --> 21:10.276
YES, YOU DO.

21:10.276 --> 21:12.546
AND THIS TIME, DEAR FRIEND,

21:12.546 --> 21:15.015
I WOULD APPRECIATE IT
IF YOU WOULD FILL ME IN ON IT.

21:15.015 --> 21:16.850
DON'T I ALWAYS?

21:16.850 --> 21:19.019
NO, YOU DON'T ALWAYS, DAVID,
BECAUSE IF YOU DID,

21:19.019 --> 21:21.421
WE WOULD NOT HAVE FOUND
OURSELVES IN THIS PREDICAMENT.

21:23.489 --> 21:24.825
NOW, HOLD ON.

21:24.825 --> 21:27.561
DID YOU JUST SAY THAT
TO ME?

21:27.561 --> 21:30.363
YES, I SAID THAT TO YOU
IN MY OFFICE ON THIS COUCH.

21:30.363 --> 21:31.965
NO, JIM.

21:31.965 --> 21:33.900
IF YOU WEREN'T SLEEPING
WITH THE WHORE,

21:33.900 --> 21:36.570
THEN WE WOULDN'T BE
IN THIS SITUATION.

21:36.570 --> 21:39.005
DON'T CALL HER THAT ANYMORE,
DAVID.

21:39.005 --> 21:40.040
OH.

21:40.040 --> 21:42.408
WHAT WOULD YOU PREFER?
PROSTITUTE?

21:42.408 --> 21:45.178
SHE'S NOT DOING THAT ANYMORE.

21:45.178 --> 21:46.547
PERHAPS SHE'S NOT,

21:46.547 --> 21:49.382
'CAUSE SHE HAS EXTORTED
ENOUGH FROM YOU

21:49.382 --> 21:51.718
TO RETIRE
FOR A YEAR OR TWO.

21:53.319 --> 21:56.189
WELL, THAT MAY BE SO.

21:57.791 --> 21:59.893
[ CHUCKLES ]

21:59.893 --> 22:01.635
YOU ARE ENJOYING THIS.

22:01.635 --> 22:02.803
[ CHUCKLES ]

22:02.803 --> 22:04.771
GRINNING LIKE
A CHESHIRE CAT.

22:04.771 --> 22:07.307
WELL...
[ CHUCKLES ]

22:07.307 --> 22:10.143
NO, YOU ‐‐
YOU NEED TO HELP ME UNDERSTAND.

22:10.143 --> 22:11.344
MM.

22:11.344 --> 22:14.014
ARE YOU TELLING ME
THAT SHE IS SO GOOD IN BED

22:14.014 --> 22:16.016
YOU ARE WILLING
TO RISK IT ALL?

22:16.016 --> 22:17.083
NO, NO.

22:17.083 --> 22:18.852
WHAT I'M TELLING YOU

22:18.852 --> 22:22.322
IS THAT SHE IS SO DAMN GOOD
AT BEING BAD

22:22.322 --> 22:25.225
THAT I WANT TO TAKE
THAT CHANCE.

22:25.225 --> 22:28.929
WELL, I CAN'T TAKE IT.

22:28.929 --> 22:31.965
I'M SORRY, DAVID.

22:31.965 --> 22:36.102
BUT HAVE YOU MET MY WIFE?

22:36.102 --> 22:38.238
AND WHAT IS THAT
SUPPOSED TO MEAN?

22:38.238 --> 22:41.708
IT MEANS KATHERYN'S IDEA
OF HAVING SEX IS NOT AT ALL.

22:44.177 --> 22:48.181
ARE YOU TELLING ME YOU NEVER
HAVE SEX WITH KATHERYN ANYMORE?

22:51.284 --> 22:54.855
[ CHUCKLES ]

22:54.855 --> 22:56.523
BITE YOUR TONGUE.

22:56.523 --> 22:58.458
NOW, HOW LONG
HAVE YOU BEEN HERE?

22:58.458 --> 23:00.160
AS LONG AS SHE'S
BEEN THERE.

23:00.160 --> 23:01.301
WHAT DOES THAT MEAN?

23:01.301 --> 23:02.769
IT MEANS THAT SHE HATES ME.

23:02.769 --> 23:05.071
SHE HATES ME, AND I DON'T
UNDERSTAND WHY.

23:05.071 --> 23:07.974
WELL, PERHAPS IT'S
BECAUSE OF YOUR ‐‐

23:07.974 --> 23:10.410
YOUR EXTRA‐CURRICULAR
ACTIVITY.

23:10.410 --> 23:11.545
NO, NO, NO.

23:11.545 --> 23:16.149
SHE'S HATED ME LONG BEFORE
I STARTED DOING THAT.

23:16.149 --> 23:18.084
AND I DON'T GET IT.

23:21.988 --> 23:23.724
TELL US.

23:25.526 --> 23:26.993
COME CLEAN, CANDACE.

23:31.898 --> 23:34.601
I'M ON MY WAY
BACK TO THE HOSPITAL.

23:34.601 --> 23:37.337
YOUR SISTER TRIED
TO COMMIT SUICIDE.

23:38.905 --> 23:40.306
WHAT?

23:41.575 --> 23:43.176
IS SHE ALL RIGHT?

23:43.176 --> 23:44.845
I DON'T KNOW.

23:44.845 --> 23:46.647
I FOUND HER IN HER BEDROOM
YESTERDAY.

23:46.647 --> 23:47.814
I CALLED 911.

23:47.814 --> 23:49.650
THEY RUSHED HER
TO THE HOSPITAL.

23:49.650 --> 23:51.084
I‐I WAS WITH HER ALL NIGHT.

23:51.084 --> 23:52.786
THE DOCTOR ASKED ME
TO COME BACK HERE

23:52.786 --> 23:54.855
TO FIND WHATEVER BOTTLES
OF PILLS THAT I COULD.

23:54.855 --> 23:56.256
WHY DIDN'T YOU CALL US?

23:56.256 --> 23:58.759
I DIDN'T HAVE TIME.

23:58.759 --> 24:00.393
I'M CALLING MY DAD.
NO, NO, NO, NO!

24:00.393 --> 24:02.669
YOU ‐‐
NO, YOU DON'T NEED TO DO THAT.

24:02.669 --> 24:04.137
WHY?

24:06.139 --> 24:08.341
AMANDA WOULDN'T WANT HIM
TO KNOW.

24:08.341 --> 24:10.844
YOU DON'T KNOW MY SISTER.

24:10.844 --> 24:12.546
SO, I‐I MEAN,
I DON'T THINK, UH ‐‐

24:12.546 --> 24:15.281
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]
HANG ON.

24:15.281 --> 24:16.482
WYATT.

24:16.482 --> 24:17.483
WYATT: Dad.

24:17.483 --> 24:18.885
WYATT.
YEAH, SON, LISTEN, I'M UH ‐‐

24:18.885 --> 24:20.086
Dad.

24:20.086 --> 24:22.088
AMANDA'S AT THE HOSPITAL.
SHE TRIED IT AGAIN.

24:22.088 --> 24:24.758
WHAT? WHERE?

24:24.758 --> 24:27.460
WHERE IS SHE?

24:27.460 --> 24:28.729
Candace,
what hospital?

24:28.729 --> 24:30.363
CANDACE?
WHAT'S SHE DOING THERE?

24:31.297 --> 24:32.766
I'M AT THEIR APARTMENT.

24:32.766 --> 24:33.834
Who's apartment?

24:33.834 --> 24:35.201
CANDACE AND AMANDA'S.

24:35.201 --> 24:38.238
CANDACE AND AMANDA
HAVE AN APARTMENT?

24:38.238 --> 24:39.305
Yes.

24:39.305 --> 24:42.308
WHERE IS YOUR SISTER, SON?
WHAT HOSPITAL?

24:42.308 --> 24:44.410
WHERE IS SHE?

24:44.410 --> 24:46.179
CANDACE!

24:47.914 --> 24:49.382
MERCY.

24:49.382 --> 24:51.484
MERCY, DAD.

24:51.484 --> 24:53.319
I'M ON MY WAY.

24:53.319 --> 24:54.655
IS EVERYTHING OKAY?

24:54.655 --> 24:56.590
NOTHING IS OKAY.

25:17.317 --> 25:20.086
WOULD YOU STOP PACING?
YOU'RE MAKING ME NERVOUS.

25:20.086 --> 25:22.022
I'M SORRY.

25:22.022 --> 25:24.958
DO YOU KNOW THE STREET VALUE
OF A KILO OF COCAINE?

25:24.958 --> 25:27.460
MY SON WOULD NOT
SELL DRUGS.

25:27.460 --> 25:30.230
WELL, YOU WERE BEHIND
ON ALL OF YOUR BILLS.

25:30.230 --> 25:32.032
LIKE A LOT OF PEOPLE.

25:33.567 --> 25:36.036
WELL, A LOT OF PEOPLE
ARE NOT ON TRIAL.

25:36.036 --> 25:37.403
YOUR SON IS.

25:37.403 --> 25:39.740
PAYING YOUR BILLS,

25:39.740 --> 25:42.676
IF HE LOVES YOU
AS MUCH AS YOU SAY HE DOES,

25:42.676 --> 25:43.977
WOULD BE A MOTIVE.

25:43.977 --> 25:48.281
MY SON WOULD NOT SELL DRUGS,
MRS. HARRINGTON.

25:48.281 --> 25:52.919
YES, YOU SAID THAT...
OVER AND OVER AGAIN.

25:52.919 --> 25:54.120
IT'S THE TRUTH.

25:54.120 --> 25:56.289
THAT SHOULD BE ENOUGH.
WELL, THE TRUTH HERE

25:56.289 --> 25:59.059
IS IN DIRECT CONTRADICTION
TO THE FACTS.

25:59.059 --> 26:00.867
THEY WERE IN
MY DAUGHTER'S CAR.

26:00.867 --> 26:01.935
HE WAS DRIVING.

26:01.935 --> 26:03.203
I DON'T SEE
HOW THIS IS HELPING.

26:03.203 --> 26:05.606
I'M ONLY ASKING THE QUESTIONS
THE PROSECUTION WOULD ASK.

26:05.606 --> 26:07.608
ARE YOU?

26:07.608 --> 26:08.809
YES.

26:08.809 --> 26:10.644
WHAT DO YOU THINK I'M DOING?
I'M TRYING TO HELP YOU.

26:10.644 --> 26:11.945
THEN DO IT.

26:11.945 --> 26:16.216
IS THAT THE WAY YOU THANK
SOMEONE WHO'S DOING YOU A FAVOR?

26:16.216 --> 26:17.450
A FAVOR?

26:17.450 --> 26:18.619
YES.

26:18.619 --> 26:20.286
WHAT DO YOU THINK IT IS?

26:20.286 --> 26:25.225
MY RATE IS $750 AN HOUR
WITH A $10,000 RETAINER.

26:25.225 --> 26:28.261
NOW, IF YOU THINK
YOU CAN AFFORD THAT,

26:28.261 --> 26:31.231
THEN [CHUCKLES]
PLEASE, HAND IT OVER.

26:31.231 --> 26:35.929
I KNOW YOU DON'T LIKE ME,
BUT WHAT IS IT?

26:37.571 --> 26:40.206
AM I TOO BLACK?

26:40.206 --> 26:44.044
IS IT 'CAUSE I'M A MAID?

26:44.044 --> 26:45.478
WHAT?

26:48.381 --> 26:51.184
WHY ARE YOU A MAID?

26:51.184 --> 26:56.322
I MEAN, OUR PEOPLE STOPPED DOING
DOMESTIC WORK IN THE '60s.

26:56.322 --> 26:57.991
HMM.

26:57.991 --> 26:59.593
APPARENTLY,
YOU DIDN'T GET THE MEMO.

26:59.593 --> 27:01.835
WHAT MEMO IS THAT?

27:01.835 --> 27:04.571
THAT WE COULD HAVE
ANYTHING WE WANT,

27:04.571 --> 27:07.407
THAT WE WERE GOOD ENOUGH,

27:07.407 --> 27:11.945
THAT EDUCATION WAS AVAILABLE
TO ALL OF US.

27:11.945 --> 27:14.414
OPTIONS WERE LIMITLESS.

27:14.414 --> 27:17.951
IT'S SO EASY FOR YOU
TO SIT THERE AND ASSUME

27:17.951 --> 27:20.554
THAT I'M IN THIS POSITION
'CAUSE I WANT TO BE.

27:20.554 --> 27:22.322
PLEASE, DON'T TELL ME.

27:22.322 --> 27:24.357
YOU'RE ONE OF THOSE PEOPLE

27:24.357 --> 27:27.528
THAT PLACES ALL THE BLAME
ON "THE MAN"?

27:27.528 --> 27:28.829
[ CHUCKLES ]

27:28.829 --> 27:30.496
NOPE.

27:33.634 --> 27:36.570
I PLACE THE BLAME
ON MYSELF.

27:36.570 --> 27:43.076
I HAD TWO BABIES ON MY HIP
AND I WORKED TWO JOBS,

27:43.076 --> 27:47.447
ONE OF THEM BEING A MAID,
WHICH I'M GOOD AT.

27:47.447 --> 27:51.317
I'M NOT ASHAMED OF,
JUST LIKE MY MAMA.

27:51.317 --> 27:54.888
THIS IS MY LIFE,
MRS. HARRINGTON.

27:54.888 --> 27:57.490
AND I'M SORRY IF I'M
ONE OF THOSE NEGROES

27:57.490 --> 28:00.260
WHO MAKES YOU REFLECT
ON WHERE WE COME FROM,

28:00.260 --> 28:02.135
OR HOW YOU WERE
SO BUSY OVERCOMING

28:02.135 --> 28:04.270
AND STEPPING ON SOME OF US
TO GET THERE.

28:04.270 --> 28:07.407
SOME OF US HAD TO TAKE
WHAT WE WERE GIVEN.

28:07.407 --> 28:10.511
I HAVE HAD TOUGH TIMES, TOO.

28:10.511 --> 28:13.146
BUT I PULLED MYSELF UP.

28:13.146 --> 28:15.749
SO, YOU THINK YOU DID IT
BY YOURSELF?

28:15.749 --> 28:18.852
NOBODY HELPED ME.

28:18.852 --> 28:23.023
IF YOU THINK GOD DIDN'T
LINE UP THINGS IN YOUR LIFE

28:23.023 --> 28:26.426
FOR YOU TO BE
IN THE POSITION YOU'RE IN,

28:26.426 --> 28:28.929
THEN YOU'RE A FOOL.

28:28.929 --> 28:31.031
MM.

28:31.031 --> 28:34.935
WHY DIDN'T GOD
LINE THINGS UP FOR YOU?

28:38.705 --> 28:40.974
WHO'S THE FOOL?

28:42.643 --> 28:45.646
I NEED YOUR HELP,
MRS. HARRINGTON,

28:45.646 --> 28:47.180
NOT YOUR SARCASM.

28:47.180 --> 28:49.449
WELL,
THAT COMES WITH THE DEAL.

28:49.449 --> 28:52.052
NOW, I AM HAPPY
TO RETURN TO MY HOME.

28:52.052 --> 28:53.486
PHEW!

28:53.486 --> 28:56.690
I HAVE A SPA DAY.

28:56.690 --> 28:58.592
I'M SORRY.

29:00.193 --> 29:03.269
THAT'S BETTER.

29:03.269 --> 29:06.640
NOW, I WILL TRY
TO GET HIM BAIL,

29:06.640 --> 29:09.543
BUT WITH AN OFFENSE LIKE THAT,

29:09.543 --> 29:14.080
IT COULD BE IN EXCESS
OF $100,000.

29:14.080 --> 29:15.916
CAN YOU AFFORD THAT?

29:15.916 --> 29:18.719
MAYBE I CAN PUT UP
MY HOUSE.

29:18.719 --> 29:22.055
WELL, YOU ARE AWARE THAT IF HE
DOESN'T SHOW UP TO COURT,

29:22.055 --> 29:23.590
YOU WILL LOSE YOUR HOUSE?

29:23.590 --> 29:25.258
HE WOULDN'T DO THAT.

29:25.258 --> 29:27.027
ARE YOU SO SURE?

29:27.027 --> 29:30.363
I KNOW MY SON...

29:30.363 --> 29:32.966
AS WELL AS YOU KNOW YOURS.

29:37.771 --> 29:40.874
OH. HEY.

29:40.874 --> 29:43.276
[ CHUCKLES ]
HEY, BABY.

29:43.276 --> 29:46.312
YEAH, YEAH.

29:46.312 --> 29:47.313
OH.

29:47.313 --> 29:48.348
BENNY, WHAT HAPPENED
TO YOUR FACE?

29:48.348 --> 29:49.449
I'M OKAY.

29:49.449 --> 29:50.984
NO, YOU'RE NOT.
WHAT HAPPENED TO YOU?

29:50.984 --> 29:52.519
I GOT INTO IT
WITH SOMEBODY DOWN HERE.

29:52.519 --> 29:53.587
I'M ALL RIGHT.

29:53.587 --> 29:54.955
BENNY.

29:54.955 --> 29:56.790
I'M ALL RIGHT, MOM.

29:58.458 --> 29:59.860
HI.

29:59.860 --> 30:02.736
HI.

30:02.736 --> 30:05.972
I'M VERONICA,
YOUR LAWYER.

30:05.972 --> 30:09.042
MAMA,
WE CAN'T AFFORD A LAWYER.

30:09.042 --> 30:10.544
I GOT IT COVERED.

30:10.544 --> 30:12.245
YOU'RE NOT PUTTING
YOUR HOUSE UP FOR ME.

30:12.245 --> 30:13.614
ARE YOU CRAZY?

30:13.614 --> 30:15.115
YOUR SISTER
GOT YOU IN THIS.

30:15.115 --> 30:17.684
I GOT TO GET YOU OUT, BABY.
THAT'S ALL THERE IS TO IT.

30:17.684 --> 30:20.253
PLEASE, LISTEN TO ME.
PLEASE.

30:20.253 --> 30:21.655
IT'S FINE.

30:21.655 --> 30:24.324
SHE'S DOING IT FOR FREE.

30:28.094 --> 30:30.163
[ Voice breaking ]
AIN'T GOD GOOD?

30:30.163 --> 30:31.598
YOU ARE?

30:31.598 --> 30:33.499
YES.

30:36.537 --> 30:38.939
THANK YOU SO MUCH.

30:38.939 --> 30:41.174
I CAN'T TELL YOU HOW MUCH
THIS MEANS TO OUR FAMILY.

30:42.976 --> 30:45.779
OKAY.

30:45.779 --> 30:47.380
YOU WANT TO TELL ME
WHAT HAPPENED?

30:47.380 --> 30:48.615
OF COURSE.

30:48.615 --> 30:52.085
I MEAN, UM...WELL,
WHERE DO YOU WANT TO START?

30:52.085 --> 30:55.522
HOW ABOUT
THE BEGINNING?

30:55.522 --> 30:57.157
OKAY,
I WAS ON MY WAY TO GET DARCI,

30:57.157 --> 30:58.592
AND I GOT PULLED OVER,
AND ‐‐

30:58.592 --> 31:00.293
WHO IS DARCI?

31:00.293 --> 31:01.535
A DATE THAT I HAD.

31:01.535 --> 31:04.605
REAL NICE GIRL
FROM THE CHURCH.

31:04.605 --> 31:05.839
AND, UM ‐‐

31:05.839 --> 31:07.073
CONTINUE.

31:07.073 --> 31:09.676
UH, THE DOGS ‐‐ THE DOGS WERE
HITTING ON THE CAR,

31:09.676 --> 31:12.278
THE COPS SAID, AND THEY PULLED
ME OUT OF THE CAR,

31:12.278 --> 31:14.480
SAID I WAS SPEEDING.

31:22.923 --> 31:25.225
Woman:
<i>PAGING DR. BENDER.</i>

31:25.225 --> 31:26.827
WYATT.

31:26.827 --> 31:27.894
DAD.

31:27.894 --> 31:29.095
WHERE IS SHE?

31:29.095 --> 31:30.163
THEY'RE NOT LETTING ANYONE
SEE HER.

31:30.163 --> 31:31.264
WHAT HAPPENED?

31:31.264 --> 31:33.066
I CAME HOME AND FOUND HER
IN HER BEDROOM.

31:33.066 --> 31:34.935
APPARENTLY, SHE HAD TAKEN
A BUNCH OF PILLS.

31:34.935 --> 31:36.503
WHAT DO YOU MEAN
YOU CAME HOME?

31:37.738 --> 31:39.472
HOW LONG YOU AND AMANDA
BEEN LIVING TOGETHER?

31:39.472 --> 31:41.374
NOT LONG.

31:42.676 --> 31:45.078
SHE'S A PROSTITUTE, DAD.

31:45.078 --> 31:46.580
SHE DID THIS.

31:47.681 --> 31:50.817
YOU NEED TO HAVE HER
ARRESTED.

31:50.817 --> 31:53.019
JUST CALM DOWN.
NO, DAD.

31:53.019 --> 31:54.254
I SAW HER ONLINE.

31:54.254 --> 31:56.790
SHE HAD AMANDA
DOING THE SAME THING.

31:56.790 --> 31:57.991
SHE'S AN ESCORT.

31:57.991 --> 31:59.492
WHAT?
WYATT, WE DON'T KNOW THAT.

31:59.492 --> 32:01.134
YES, I DO.

32:01.134 --> 32:04.270
MR. CRYER, WE DON'T HAVE
ANY PROOF OF THAT.

32:04.270 --> 32:06.072
IS THAT TRUE?

32:07.808 --> 32:09.743
THEN HOW COME MY SON
IS SAYING IT?

32:09.743 --> 32:11.144
WHY DO YOU THINK
THAT SHE HAS YOUR SISTER

32:11.144 --> 32:12.278
DOING THE SAME THING?

32:12.278 --> 32:14.014
SHE IS EVIL.

32:14.014 --> 32:15.649
NOW, I KNOW WHAT SHE'S
TRYING TO DO.

32:15.649 --> 32:19.085
PRETENDING TO WANT TO STUDY,
TRYING TO SEDUCE YOU.

32:20.654 --> 32:21.955
SHE IS EVIL.

32:21.955 --> 32:24.591
WYATT, CALM DOWN.

32:25.559 --> 32:26.860
WHERE ARE THE DOCTORS?

32:26.860 --> 32:28.094
THEY'RE IN THERE WITH HER.

32:28.094 --> 32:30.363
THEY SAID THEY'LL BE OUT HERE
SOON TO TALK TO US.

32:30.363 --> 32:31.565
DID YOU CALL YOUR MOTHER?

32:31.565 --> 32:34.000
SHE'S NOT ANSWERING.

32:34.000 --> 32:37.403
WELL, THAT'S GREAT.

32:37.403 --> 32:38.639
JUST GREAT.

32:38.639 --> 32:40.173
SHE'LL BE OKAY.

32:46.713 --> 32:48.515
HI.

32:48.515 --> 32:49.750
HI.

32:49.750 --> 32:52.018
UM, SORRY.

32:52.018 --> 32:55.689
WE'LL BE OUT OF YOUR HAIR
IN JUST A SECOND.

32:55.689 --> 32:58.859
HOW'S IT GOING?

32:58.859 --> 33:02.536
I MET HANNA'S SON.

33:02.536 --> 33:05.238
HOW DID IT GO?

33:05.238 --> 33:08.241
I THINK
HE'S TELLING THE TRUTH.

33:08.241 --> 33:09.676
HONEY.
NO, SWEETHEART.

33:09.676 --> 33:11.411
SOMETHING IS REALLY WRONG,

33:11.411 --> 33:13.947
AND THE DETECTIVE
THAT ARRESTED HIM,

33:13.947 --> 33:16.116
I'M SURE
HE'S NOT ABOVE BOARD.

33:16.116 --> 33:17.684
RANKINS.

33:17.684 --> 33:18.952
YEAH.

33:18.952 --> 33:20.353
YOU KNOW HIM?

33:20.353 --> 33:21.688
YES.

33:21.688 --> 33:24.357
WELL, MAYBE YOU CAN GET HIM
TO RETURN MY PHONE CALL

33:24.357 --> 33:25.626
SINCE HE HADN'T ALL DAY.

33:25.626 --> 33:27.728
I'LL GIVE HIM A CALL.

33:27.728 --> 33:30.296
THANKS.

33:30.296 --> 33:33.967
SOMETHING
IS REALLY WRONG HERE.

33:33.967 --> 33:36.703
BUT YOU KNOW YOUR WIFE.

33:36.703 --> 33:37.938
[ CHUCKLES ]

33:37.938 --> 33:40.874
I WILL GET
TO THE BOTTOM OF IT.

33:40.874 --> 33:43.677
YEAH, SWEETHEART.

33:43.677 --> 33:46.580
I'M SURE YOU WILL.

33:46.580 --> 33:50.884
UM, I WAS JUST ON MY WAY
TO THE HOSPITAL.

33:50.884 --> 33:53.053
IT'S AMANDA.

33:55.088 --> 33:56.823
SHE TRIED IT AGAIN.

33:56.823 --> 33:59.125
OH, DAVID.

33:59.125 --> 34:01.267
LET'S GO.

34:01.267 --> 34:02.936
JUST TELLING ME THIS.

34:05.405 --> 34:08.408
I'LL LEAVE THE REST.
LET'S GO.

34:20.787 --> 34:23.824
Woman: <i>DR. BENDER</i>
<i>TO THE MEDICAL WARD.</i>

34:23.824 --> 34:25.759
<i>DR. BENDER.</i>

34:35.235 --> 34:37.337
[ SIGHS ]

34:37.337 --> 34:40.340
ALL RIGHT, GUYS.
I'M GONNA GO.

34:40.340 --> 34:43.544
LET ME KNOW
IF SOMETHING CHANGES.

34:43.544 --> 34:45.612
SURE.
JUST GET OUT OF HERE.

34:54.020 --> 34:56.890
I KNOW THIS IS
REALLY HARD FOR YOU.

35:01.501 --> 35:04.370
NO ONE OUTSIDE OF THE FAMILY
KNEW IT.

35:06.773 --> 35:09.776
I FOUND HER
THE FIRST TIME.

35:09.776 --> 35:12.746
I'M SO SORRY.

35:12.746 --> 35:16.316
I FOUND HER
IN THE BATHROOM.

35:16.316 --> 35:19.653
WHY DO YOU THINK
SHE DID IT?

35:27.528 --> 35:30.130
SHE'S BEEN UNHAPPY SINCE.

35:30.130 --> 35:33.667
SHE'S BEEN UNHAPPY
SINCE WHAT?

35:33.667 --> 35:37.804
WE WERE LEFT AT SUMMER CAMP,

35:37.804 --> 35:42.943
AND, UH,
IT WAS WITH THE CHURCH.

35:42.943 --> 35:45.879
AND...

35:48.481 --> 35:51.685
AND WHAT?

35:51.685 --> 35:56.356
FATHER ELAMOS.

35:56.356 --> 35:58.692
YOU REMEMBER HIM?

35:58.692 --> 35:59.760
YEAH.

36:03.570 --> 36:05.972
IT'S OKAY. IT'S OKAY.

36:07.674 --> 36:09.976
HE MADE US DO THINGS.

36:12.445 --> 36:14.581
WHAT KIND OF THINGS?

36:16.182 --> 36:19.385
[ SIGHS DEEPLY ]

36:19.385 --> 36:20.887
I DON'T WANT TO TALK ABOUT IT,
OKAY?

36:20.887 --> 36:23.489
NO, IT'S...WYATT, IT'S OKAY.

36:23.489 --> 36:25.358
I THINK YOU SHOULD.

36:25.358 --> 36:29.229
THIS IS WHAT WE'VE BEEN
WORKING TOWARDS.

36:29.229 --> 36:31.798
THINK TALKING ABOUT THIS
WOULD REALLY HELP YOU.

36:34.535 --> 36:36.469
[ SIGHS ]

36:39.706 --> 36:41.875
LAURA.
HI.

36:41.875 --> 36:43.977
HI.
HI.

36:49.315 --> 36:51.752
HOW ARE YOU?

36:51.752 --> 36:53.687
FINE.

36:53.687 --> 36:56.156
I HEARD ABOUT AMANDA.

36:56.156 --> 36:57.891
I'M SO SORRY.

36:57.891 --> 37:01.234
LAURA.

37:01.234 --> 37:02.368
HI, JEFFREY.

37:02.368 --> 37:03.369
HI.

37:03.369 --> 37:04.738
HOW ARE YOU?

37:04.738 --> 37:06.773
GOOD.

37:06.773 --> 37:09.743
I‐I CAME DOWN AS SOON AS I HEARD
ABOUT AMANDA.

37:09.743 --> 37:12.011
YEAH, WELL,
IT'S JUST FAMILY NOW.

37:12.011 --> 37:13.379
IT'S PRETTY PRIVATE.

37:13.379 --> 37:16.783
OKAY.
YEAH, I‐I UNDERSTAND.

37:18.585 --> 37:19.953
HEY, HEY.

37:19.953 --> 37:21.688
I'M SO SORRY.

37:21.688 --> 37:24.257
I'M SO SORRY.

37:29.062 --> 37:30.597
I MISSED YOU SO MUCH.

37:30.597 --> 37:32.132
YOU KNOW WHAT, WYATT?

37:32.132 --> 37:34.635
WE SHOULD PROBABLY BE
GETTING BACK INSIDE.

37:37.137 --> 37:38.672
HOLD ON.

37:43.243 --> 37:45.478
HOW HAVE YOU BEEN?

37:45.478 --> 37:48.949
MISSING YOU.

37:48.949 --> 37:50.784
I'M SORRY.

37:50.784 --> 37:53.820
I WANT TO APOLOGIZE.

37:53.820 --> 37:57.357
I...DON'T BE MAD AT ME.

37:57.357 --> 37:59.225
[ CHUCKLES ]

37:59.225 --> 38:02.503
I COULD NEVER BE MAD AT YOU.
I LOVE YOU TOO MUCH.

38:02.503 --> 38:04.571
I'M DOING BETTER.

38:04.571 --> 38:06.439
RIGHT, JEFFREY?

38:06.439 --> 38:10.410
YES, AND WE'D LIKE TO KEEP IT
THAT WAY, SO COME ON.

38:10.410 --> 38:12.746
CAN YOU VISIT ME?

38:12.746 --> 38:15.849
UH, WHERE?

38:15.849 --> 38:18.084
I HAVE 30 DAYS LEFT.

38:18.084 --> 38:22.455
IT WOULD BE REALLY NICE
TO SEE A FRIEND.

38:22.455 --> 38:24.290
Jeffrey: NO. NO, NO, NO, NO, NO.
CAN'T DO THAT.

38:24.290 --> 38:26.026
THAT'S AGAINST THE RULES,
WYATT.

38:26.026 --> 38:28.995
NOT FOR THE LAST TWO WEEKS.

38:28.995 --> 38:30.130
PLEASE.

38:30.130 --> 38:31.932
I WILL.
OKAY.

38:31.932 --> 38:35.135
ALL RIGHT, COME ON, WYATT.

38:35.135 --> 38:38.304
I LOVE YOU.
I LOVE YOU SO MUCH.

38:38.304 --> 38:40.273
COME ON, WYATT.

38:44.210 --> 38:46.212
[ SIGHS ]

38:48.148 --> 38:49.315
MM.

38:49.315 --> 38:51.484
YOU'RE UP.

38:51.484 --> 38:53.453
YEAH.

38:53.453 --> 38:55.889
YOUR PHONE'S
BEEN RINGING.

38:55.889 --> 38:58.792
I DON'T CARE.
TURN IT OFF.

38:58.792 --> 39:01.367
IT COULD BE IMPORTANT.

39:01.367 --> 39:05.005
WHAT'S MORE IMPORTANT THAN
GETTING HEALED FROM THIS CANCER?

39:05.005 --> 39:06.039
MM.

39:06.039 --> 39:08.575
NOW,
THAT'S THE RIGHT IDEA.

39:08.575 --> 39:11.211
HOW'D IT GO WITH VERONICA?

39:11.211 --> 39:13.379
FINE.

39:13.379 --> 39:14.748
HANNA.

39:14.748 --> 39:17.383
NO, IT WAS FINE.

39:17.383 --> 39:18.852
SHE WASN'T MEAN TO YOU?

39:18.852 --> 39:20.721
WHY WOULD YOU SAY THAT?

39:20.721 --> 39:24.424
'CAUSE I'VE KNOWN HER
FOR YEARS.

39:24.424 --> 39:26.326
SHE CAN GET THE JOB DONE.

39:26.326 --> 39:27.661
YEAH, I HOPE SO.

39:27.661 --> 39:29.996
I DON'T KNOW HOW MUCH MORE
OF THIS MY SON CAN TAKE.

39:29.996 --> 39:32.032
[ GRUNTS ]

39:32.032 --> 39:33.900
YOU OKAY?
[ GRUNTS ]

39:33.900 --> 39:37.303
I'M ‐‐ I'M NOT FEELING TOO WELL
RIGHT NOW, HANNA.

39:37.303 --> 39:38.939
CALL THE NURSE, PLEASE.

39:38.939 --> 39:40.006
YEAH.

39:40.006 --> 39:42.543
AND THEN I WANT YOU
TO GO HOME.

39:42.543 --> 39:43.744
NO.

39:43.744 --> 39:45.846
YES.
THIS IS TOO MUCH.

39:45.846 --> 39:47.413
I'M NOT GONNA LEAVE YOU
RIGHT NOW.

39:47.413 --> 39:49.415
I'M FINE.
OHH.

39:49.415 --> 39:50.884
THANK YOU, HANNA.

39:50.884 --> 39:52.553
YEAH.

39:52.553 --> 39:55.622
THANK YOU.

39:55.622 --> 40:00.527
I HOPE THAT YOUR CHILDREN ARE
AS GOOD TO PEOPLE AS YOU ARE.

40:00.527 --> 40:03.036
WELL,
ONE OF THEM IS FOR SURE.

40:03.036 --> 40:04.237
MM.

40:06.239 --> 40:07.508
MM.

40:10.677 --> 40:13.446
MM.

40:15.348 --> 40:17.417
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

40:17.417 --> 40:19.019
MR. CRYER.

40:19.019 --> 40:21.421
WYATT'S OUT HERE
FALLING ASLEEP,

40:21.421 --> 40:23.056
SO WE'RE JUST GONNA
HEAD BACK TO THE HOUSE.

40:23.056 --> 40:27.728
GOOD. I'LL SEE YOU, UH...
I'LL SEE YOU ALL THERE LATER.

40:27.728 --> 40:29.796
OKAY.

40:29.796 --> 40:31.497
AND WE'LL BE BACK
IN THE MORNING.

40:31.497 --> 40:32.666
FINE.

40:32.666 --> 40:35.702
AND MY PARENTS SHOULD BE HERE
ANY MINUTE.

40:35.702 --> 40:37.738
THAT'S GOOD.
THANKS.

40:37.738 --> 40:39.606
[ SNIFFLES ]

40:39.606 --> 40:41.307
HEY, JEFFREY.

40:41.307 --> 40:42.609
YES, SIR?

40:42.609 --> 40:46.613
DO YOU HAVE
CANDACE'S ADDRESS?

40:46.613 --> 40:48.314
YES, SIR.

40:51.217 --> 40:52.786
I'D LIKE YOU
TO WRITE IT DOWN

40:52.786 --> 40:55.421
AND AND PUT IT ON THE TABLE
OVER THERE FOR ME, PLEASE.

40:55.421 --> 40:56.623
SURE.

40:58.491 --> 41:02.302
TELL WYATT WHEN HE WAKES UP
THAT HIS FATHER LOVES HIM.

41:02.302 --> 41:03.970
I WILL, MR. CRYER.

41:06.807 --> 41:08.909
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

41:20.787 --> 41:23.189
[ POUNDING ON DOOR ]

41:28.929 --> 41:30.597
YOU COME AFTER
MY DAUGHTER?

41:30.597 --> 41:33.499
WHAT ARE YOU GONNA DO
ABOUT IT?

41:36.402 --> 41:39.573
<i>NEXT ON "THE HAVES</i>
<i>AND THE HAVE NOTS"...</i>

41:39.573 --> 41:41.808
I DIDN'T KNOW HOW MUCH I'D GROW
TO LIKE YOU, WYATT.

41:41.808 --> 41:43.476
LAURA,
YOU REMEMBER JEFFREY.

41:43.476 --> 41:46.012
I DON'T WANT YOU TO RELAPSE,
AND SHE WILL MAKE YOU RELAPSE.

41:46.012 --> 41:47.313
I DON'T WANT THAT.

41:47.313 --> 41:48.749
YOU PRAY FOR ME.

41:48.749 --> 41:49.816
I WILL.

41:49.816 --> 41:51.618
I DID IT AGAIN.

41:51.618 --> 41:54.120
TRIED TO HURT YOURSELF AGAIN,
BABY.

41:54.120 --> 41:55.455
I'M SORRY.

